Package: sparsevector
Type: Package
Title: Sparse Numeric Vectors for Efficient Computation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Anthony", 
           family = "Yang", 
           email = "anthonyang2027@utexas.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an S4 class 'sparse_numeric' to represent sparse numeric vectors efficiently,
    along with arithmetic operations, cross-products, norms, and standardization methods.
    Designed for memory-efficient storage and computation on vectors with many zeros.
